cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.CL

The paper deals with the recognition of handwritten input, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of classification algorithms such as SVM, KNN and Neural Network suggests that the paper may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper may also involve information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques for processing handwritten documents, and natural language processing (cs.CL) for interpreting the handwritten text.
